@startuml
title Room Assignment Sequence

actor Admin
participant "Qt GUI" as GUI
participant "University" as University
participant "Dormitory" as Dormitory
participant "Room" as Room
participant "Student" as Student

Admin -> GUI: choose student, dormitory, room
GUI -> University: assignStudentToRoom(studentId, dormitoryId, roomNumber)
University -> University: find Student and Dormitory
University -> Dormitory: assignStudent(student, roomNumber)
Dormitory -> Room: addStudent(studentId)
Room -> Room: check capacity and duplicates
Room --> Dormitory: student accepted
Dormitory -> Student: assignToRoom(dormitoryId, roomNumber)
Student --> Dormitory: assignment saved
Dormitory --> University: assignment complete
University --> GUI: success
GUI --> Admin: show updated room and student status

@enduml
